GitLab’s latest release uses AI for more than just making code completion smarter, with customisable agents, a Knowledge Graph, and more. A developer’s day is often a constant juggle. You’re not just writing code; you’re deciphering legacy systems, navigating complex dependencies, wrestling with pipelines, and trying to remember your team’s specific, unwritten rules for formatting […]

title: GitLab launches custom AI agents and Knowledge Graph
